font-manager: A font management application for the GNOME desktop
font-manager:
font-manager: Font Manager is not intended to be a professional-grade font management
font-manager: solution, but rather a simple application suitable for the needs of most
font-manager: desktop users, and even some graphics designers who may need to manage
font-manager: just a few thousand font files.
font-manager: 
font-manager: Although designed with the GNOME desktop environment in mind, it should
font-manager: work well with most major desktop environments such as Xfce,
font-manager: Enlightenment, and even KDE.
font-manager: 
font-manager: Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/font-manager/
